===================
*     README      *
===================

1. Install

	a. Requirements:
	  - i686, ppc, SPARC, etc.
		- g++ >= 3.x
		- freeling 2.0 
		- lttoolbox 2.0
		- libxml2 (last version)
		- gnu make

	b. Building & installing
		$ ./configure
		$ make
		# make install

For build options, please see the INSTALL file.
